&& apt remove build-essential -y \
&& apt autoremove -y \
&& mkdir /root/.netease-musicbox/ \

CMD cd /usr/src/app \
&& exec gunicorn nem_parser.wsgi:application \
    --bind 0.0.0.0:80 \
    --workers 2
